title: Scivation Xtend Go Amino Energy BCAA Powder for Pre Workout or Anytime Energy, BCAAs, Blue Raspberry, 30 Servings
description: XTEND GO™ + Amino Energy BCAA powder is the perfect supplement to promote focus and energy, while also supplying branched-chain amino acids that are critical for muscle growth support and recovery.XTEND GO™ contains 7g of BCAAs — in the nature-designed and widely-researched 2:1:1 ratio — along with Glutamine and Citrulline Malate. Plus, with hydration-promoting electrolytes, XTEND GO™ BCAA powder is the delicious, refreshing, sugar-free way to help anyone grind through a tough morning, a brutal workday, or a grueling gym session.Designed for intra-workout consumption, and also highly functional both before and after training, XTEND GO™ contains an effective combination of caffeine and L-Theanine that enhances intensity, focus, and energy. No pre-workout jitters, no energy-drink crash, no fats or sugars from an overloaded coffee – just a clean way to squeeze the most out of your day.
